{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_52_03",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 3話 幽霊怖いーー！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃっ、なんですかあの音は～\nちょっと{user}さん待って下さい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yipe! what was that sound~\nWait‚ {user}-san‚ please…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.9999999999995,
          "startTime": 3.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2645804405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに速く歩いたら迷子になっちゃうじゃないですか\n……えっと、{user}さんがですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you walk so fast‚ I’ll get lost!\n…I mean‚ you will‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "一本道だから、迷子になる心配はないと思うが……\n……そ、それにしても……雰囲気出てるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a straight path‚ so I don’t think we’ll get lost…\nS-still… this place has quite the atmosphere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2790909223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さすが世界最恐のお化け屋敷だ\n……こころだって怖いよな。そんなにくっついて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of the world’s scariest haunted house.\n…You’re scared too‚ right? You’re clinging so close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9153287569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "……は、はぁ～？　怖くなんかありませんけど？\nこんなの、子供騙しじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…H-huh~? I’m not scared at all‚ okay?\nThis is just child’s play.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1752835273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "仕掛けだって、言うほど凝ってもいませんし！\nほらっ、全然平気ですっ……ひぃやぁ～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The tricks aren’t even that elaborate!\nSee? I’m totally fine… hiyyaaah~~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.941950194,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gisi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5248.934491500002,
          "startTime": 46.4086168606
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.641950194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、今の悲鳴は、ただの気合いの掛け声です\n悲鳴じゃありませんからノーカウントです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that scream was just a battle cry.\nNot a scream‚ so it doesn’t count!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3086168606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.1644212722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりこんな所で気合いを入れないでくれ\n……あのさ、さっき言いかけた話だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t suddenly shout something like that in a place like this.\nAnyway… about what I was saying earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.222733638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "へ？　……あぁ、このアトラクションの\n怖い噂ってやつですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? …Ah‚ the scary rumor\nabout this attraction?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1994101841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.8532873153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、噂で聞いたんだ。このアトラクションは\n以前墓地だった場所に建てられているらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I heard a rumor. This attraction\nwas apparently built on what used to be a cemetery.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、たまに本物の幽霊が出るとか……\nもしかして、愛もその噂を知ってたんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So sometimes real ghosts appear there…\nMaybe Ai knew that rumor too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.7544890086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そ、そんな噂があったんですかぁ！？\nうぎゃああぁぁ！　なんですか、今の音はっ？！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-th-there was a rumor like that!?\nUgyyaaaaah!! W-what was that sound just now!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7339452107,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_horror-voice-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4412.789535499996,
          "startTime": 90.1672785441
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うわあっ！　……こ、こころの悲鳴の方が\n心臓に悪いんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uwaa! …K-Kokoro‚ your scream\nis worse for my heart…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5726.411024899989,
          "startTime": 99.6333307903
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.6333307903
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.7307175319
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "……うっ、こころ、立てません……\n足が動かなくなっちゃいました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh‚ Kokoro… can’t stand…\nMy legs won’t move anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7910808881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ？　もしかしてこれがあの有名な\n金縛りってやつ……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…H-huh? Could this be that famous\nsleep paralysis…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1577475548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.5887446721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "いやだぁー！　幽霊怖いーー！\nもう外に出たいですーー！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Noooo! Ghosts are scaryyy!\nI wanna get out of here alreadyyy!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9369101953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころ、落ち着いてくれ\n多分腰が抜けただけだから。ほら、深呼吸をして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kokoro‚ calm down.\nYour legs probably just gave out. Come on‚ take a deep breath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.926862669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "……！　{user}さん、う、う、後ろに\nゆ、ゆ、ゆ…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…! {user}-san‚ b-b-behind you—\nGho-gh-gh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どうした、こころ？\nゆ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What is it‚ Kokoro?\nGho…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3621741693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.7385630608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "ぎいやぁああああああ！\nこころを食べないで下さ～～い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Giiyaaaaaaaaah!!\nPlease don’t eat Kokoro~!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3476310254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "食べるなら{user}さんで\nお願いしま～す！　プリ～～～ズ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re going to eat someone‚\neat {user}-san~! Pleeeeeease!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4266592821,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.666666700013,
          "startTime": 150.2933259488
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.8933259488
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hauntedhouse-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.3021889686
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころ、待ってくれ！\n俺を置いて行かないでくれ～～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kokoro‚ wait!\nDon’t leave me behind~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7426554407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 160.3099439938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……もうお化け屋敷はこりごりです\n幽霊にも、二度と会いたくないです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I’ve had enough of haunted houses.\nI never want to see a ghost again~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5677456062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
